## 3. ΣCard for Agents

Agent streams (agent-generated data) are registered in the MatrixRegistry like any other
stream. The key difference: all agent paths live under `{platform}.agent.*` and are
automatically tagged `data_class: "inferred"`.

Agents must not write to `{platform}.nav.*`, `{platform}.engine.*` etc. directly.
They write to `{platform}.cmd.*` paths and `{platform}.agent.*` paths only.

